      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCe65137d82e4d1005838ac272b5ad609c"></a>Adjusting the idle speed
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/note.jpg">Note
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4182"> </a>Check that the bike is provided with electronic control unit, original intake and exhaust systems, otherwise fit original
         components.
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4185"> </a>Connect the inserts of exhaust gas analyser (5) no. <span class="bold">88713.1010</span> to the outlets on the exhaust pipes using unions (5).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_6_008404078.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4193"> </a>Make sure that the throttle body pulley is seated against the anti-stitching screw (throttle control completely closed).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4195"> </a>Make sure that the throttle cable free play is correctly adjusted.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4198"> </a>Check:
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4202"> </a>that throttle angle reading with engine off is 0°.
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4205"> </a>The idle rpm must be within 1,300÷1,400 rpm (1,350±50):
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4209"> </a>if the idle rpm are lower or higher than the indicated ones, open or close both cylinder by-pass screws (6) and (7) by 1/4.
                           Once the correct rpm have been reached, check that the CO value of both cylinders is higher than 0.4%.
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_6_008504079.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_6_008604080.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4217"> </a>The actions to be taken in case idle speed adjustment has not been successfully completed are the following:
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4221"> </a>inspect the cylinders (clearance, strokes, valve sealing, etc.).
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4224"> </a>Repeat the entire idle speed adjustment procedure.
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4227"> </a>Check the vacuum pressures downstream of the throttle valve (carry out this check only after completing the steps described
                           above).
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/warning.jpg">Warning
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4230"> </a>If the engine is shut off before proceeding with adjustment of the CO level, wait three minutes after restarting for the enrichment
         phase to finish and the lambda sensors to start operating.
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4233"> </a>If the idle rpm are high and the by-pass screw adjustment was not successful, check the seals under the throttle valve; in
            particular make sure that there are no cracks or cuts in the intake manifolds, that the latter are properly fixed against
            the engine, that there are not cuts in the pressure sensor hoses, etc.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/warning.jpg">Warning
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4236"> </a>Idle speed adjustment takes priority over balancing the vacuum pressures downstream of the throttle valve. Differences in
         pressure between the horizontal and vertical cylinder are therefore acceptable, provided that the idle speed is adjusted correctly.
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4240"> </a>If you are unable to attain the desired idle speed setting, try reducing the vacuum differential downstream of the throttle
                           valve.
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
         <div class="Trattino_outer" style="margin-left: 0pt;">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
               <tr style="vertical-align: baseline;">
                  <td>
                     <div class="Trattino_inner" style="width: 20pt; white-space: nowrap;">- </div>
                  </td>
                  <td width="100%">
                     <div class="Trattino_inner">
                        <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4243"> </a>Repeat the entire idle speed adjustment procedure.
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
